        "text_dKEdg6": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Bio-Cor can be used directly during or after a therapeutic session to support relaxation, grounding, and integration.</p><p>The frequency-based sound generated by Bio-Cor provides a gentle sensory framework that helps the nervous system remain receptive after therapeutic work.</p><p>This use is particularly relevant when the goal is to stabilize the effects of a session and support gradual regulation over time.</p>",
