          "settings": {
            "subheading": "Frequency-Based Sound Generation",
            "heading": "<strong>Transforming data into sound</strong>",
            "heading_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>Bio-Cor translates Bio-Well data into a structured frequency-based sound output, adapted to the individual profile.</p><p>The sound is generated automatically, without manual configuration or audio selection.</p>",
