          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "subheading": "Sound Application",
            "heading": "<strong>During or after the session</strong>",
            "heading_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>The generated sound can be used immediately during a session or provided for post-session integration.</p><p>Playback is simple and controlled, using headphones or external audio systems.</p>",
