          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Common practitioner applications include:</strong></p><ul><li>Providing personalized post-session sound support for clients</li><li>Preparing frequency-informed water for at-home continuity</li><li>Supporting integration between sessions in therapeutic follow-ups</li><li>Complementing sound-based, relaxation, or mindfulness practices</li><li>Creating structured relaxation or sleep support protocols</li><li>Enhancing grounding and stabilization phases after intensive sessions</li></ul>",
