      "name": "Final Therapeutic Summary",
      "settings": {
        "gap": "large",
        "columns": 2,
        "columns_mobile": "1",
        "swipe_on_mobile": true,
        "heading": "Extending the Therapeutic Process Beyond the Session",
        "heading_size": "title-xl tracking-heading",
        "heading_alignment": "text-center md:items-center",
        "heading_tag": "h2",
        "subheading": "",
        "description": "<p>Bio-Cor is designed to support integration, continuity, and embodiment of therapeutic work beyond the treatment room.</p><p>By combining frequency-informed sound with gentle ultra-high frequency signaling, Bio-Cor helps create conditions that favor nervous system regulation and progressive integration over time.</p><p>Bio-Cor does not replace therapy.<br/> It supports what is already taking place, allowing the therapeutic process to continue naturally and coherently between sessions.</p>",
